desc: Your music shop in the Dandenong Ranges that specialises in quality guitars both first and secondhand, with guitars from Martin, Fender, Tanglewood, Cort and more! Percussion, a vast collection of progressive and recreational sheet music and accessories. Folk instruments like accordion, banjo, mandolin and bodhran!

layout.text: At Upwey Music we stock high-quality new and vintage guitars for everyone from the beginner to the professional.
